social_posts.post_text: Filing under things I never want to forget 🎄🤍
Baby girl is going to be O N E soon + I’m not okay 😥

⭐️ ONE ⭐️

A little late but happy birthday, my sweet baby, Lu. You are such a wonder. You are sunshine, you are love, you are hope and every other beautiful thing in this life. You are everything I could have ever dreamed of and I’m so lucky you chose me to be your Mama. I can’t believe I get an entire lifetime of loving you 🤍
My first born, the one who made me a Mama. Four years ago you were placed on my chest and I finally knew…my purpose, my place, my reason. Happy 4th Birthday, my sunshine, you are such a wonder! 🤍⭐️

Keeping this masterpiece forever 🥹
